Date: Wed, 22 Apr 2026 10:21:42 +1000
Subject: [PATCH] chore(release-sync): refresh session-write-lock patch for
 v2026.4.20 base

The upstream v2026.4.20 refactored session-write-lock.ts and reverted
the write-lock backoff config. Re-apply the patch on top of the new
upstream code with the updated file structure (new watchdog helpers,
exit handler refactor, etc).
